      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>potato slices</strong> and <strong>courgette rounds </strong>to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 25-30 min or until the vegetables are golden and crisp – this is your <strong>cooked veg</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? Use 2 trays!</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
