    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> sliced onion</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>tomato paste</strong> to the pan and cook for a further 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
