        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fully coated, remove the pan from the heat and stir through your <strong>crème fraîche</strong> and most of the <strong>chopped dill </strong>(save some for garnish!) – this is your<strong> veggie ragout</strong></p><p>Once the spelt is cooked, add the<strong> remaining vegetable stock mix</strong> and <strong>chopped spinach</strong> to the pot with the cooked spelt and mix it all together – this is your <strong>spinach spelt</strong></p>",
